  %% Diagram 51: PWA, Mobile, and POS Experience Topology

  PWA[Web PWA Experience]
  Mobile[Mobile App Experience]
  POS[POS Mode Experience\nBarcode and QR assisted sales]

  API[Shared Backend APIs]
  Orders[(Orders and state)]
  Inventory[(Inventory and variants)]

  Sync[Cross-channel synchronization]
  LinkLoss{Connectivity interruption?}
  OfflineMode[Continue in constrained mode\nlocal queue for POS and cart actions]
  Resync[Reconcile on reconnect]
  Conflict{State conflict detected?}
  Resolve[Resolve conflict by latest server version plus audit marker]

  PWA --> API
  Mobile --> API
  POS --> API

  API --> Orders
  API --> Inventory
  Orders --> Sync
  Inventory --> Sync

  POS --> LinkLoss
  LinkLoss -- Yes --> OfflineMode --> Resync --> Conflict
  Conflict -- Yes --> Resolve --> API
  Conflict -- No --> API
  LinkLoss -- No --> API
